{"tid":1857382,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳確診患者糞便樣本中對新型冠狀病毒呈陽性","createTime":"2020-02-02T07:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T07:10:00.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9175708260da328078cf36da0af462a746c0bc35","tid":1857382,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:10:00.000Z","msg":"深圳市第三人民醫院的肝病研究所，在確診患者的糞便樣本中發現對新型冠狀病毒呈陽性反應，顯示病毒可能在糞便中存活。<br />\n<br />\n深圳市第三人民醫院副院長劉映霞又表示，研究人員下一步要加緊研究和分離病毒，證實是否有新型冠狀病毒在大便中存活，她呼籲民眾戴口罩的同時要勤洗手和注意個人衛生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=378935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378935&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9Gg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=3c749f88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378935&h=95daca1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=378935</a>"}]}